text: Elodie Kuijper (born 2 March 2000) is a Dutch professional racing cyclist, who rode for the UCI Women's Team . In May 2019, she signed with for the 2019 women's road cycling season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
